    {
        "desc": "A small wooden bridge spans a stream that runs between the two sections of the\nbuilding. The stream gurgles over a steep cliff, falling ever downward into the\nrolling ocean. Two small benches and a small table sit on this redwood bridge.\nThe view is commanding, and ever tempting to elves longing to sail west for\nvalinor, waiting to be greeted by their long departed brethren. To the east, the\nstream pours towards you out of a lush forest. The bridge leads to a large\nentrance hall to the north and to the more private rooms of the residence to the\nsouth.\n",
