        "desc": "This broad hall has been finely furnished with comfortable couches and chairs. A\nwide hearth lies against the north wall, while against the west wall stands what\nappears to be a huge display case. Upon closer inspection you realise it\ncontains a dazzling supply of pipes of all kinds as well as wide variety of\npipeweeds and herbs. A beautiful but tiny fountain trickles softly near the\neastern wall. The room is warm and comfortable and one could feel like resting\nhere a while.\n",
